nodes.group: A business with the goal in mind to expand on a global scale, eventually.
nodes.name: Startup

nodes.group: These startups aim to resolve problems that are commonly found in the medical services which include, hospitals, insurance, doctors, and patient relations.
nodes.name: Healthcare

nodes.group: These startups aim to resolve problems regarding crop generation, procurement, and distribution, as well as convenience issues farmers may have.
nodes.name: Agriculture

nodes.group: These startups aim to help problems inundating the drug discovery field, and tend to fall in the human therapeutics category. It aims to resolve issues in helping humans recover from ailments using a more biology based approach.
nodes.name: Biotech

nodes.group: These startups aim to make the world a more environmentally clean place. This means the transition from the wasteful practices many companies currently use to more cleaner alternatives. These can range from the purification of water, to storing energy, to making certain products more recyclable.
nodes.name: Clean Tech

nodes.group: These startups aim to create certain food or drink products or processes to help in the food and drink creation.
nodes.name: Food/drinks

nodes.group: These startups aim to help people go from location A to B in as fast, cheap and most convenient way possible. Transportation startups also include the delivery of physical goods from place A to B.
nodes.name: Transportation

nodes.group: These startups aim to help inform people regarding web related stuff. These startups can range from being a business to customer, or business to business solution.
nodes.name: Web as a service/Data Analytics

nodes.group: These startups aim to resolve issues in the manufacturing industries. They also desire to help modulate (make more modular) processes, as well as make them cheaper. Also included in this category are startups that create physical gadgets for customer use.
nodes.name: Manufacturing

nodes.group: These startups aim to resolve the financial issues people or businesses have. These companies can range from issues regarding savings, spending, investing, and general financial literacy.
nodes.name: Financial Tech

nodes.group: These startups aim to help children learn and perform better academically. They do so with the aim of not only helping the child perform better, but to actually learn better. Aside from student oriented tech, education tech also include help streamlining lesson planning/evaluation for teachers and schools.
nodes.name: Education

nodes.group: These startups aim to help people create better advertising, advertising techniques, as well as data analytics on how well previous ads did.
nodes.name: Advertising

nodes.group: These startups aim to help provide better security for customers ranging in businesses, government, and every day people. Security is provided for things ranging from online personal information and hacking protection to name a couple.
nodes.name: Security

nodes.group: These startups aim to help provide novel means of entertainment to every day consumer customers. They also aim to provide convenience in getting access to entertainment.
nodes.name: Entertainment
